name: "Pisssssss"
description:
"Pisssssss" The last part of the 3-part story,
People are so afraid of the spit that they can’t help but piss themselves. Fear of that which will never reach the land cuts these poor people off their ties to the land, That's why it's hard: why would you hold it when everyone else is releasing it?

Smell the air.

These people are standing on their piss, not on their feet.
